<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٠١-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي عَبْدُ الْمَلِكِ قَالَ:</span> قُلْتُ لِأَحْمَدَ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَيَشْتَرِي الرَّجُلُ صَدَقَةَ مَالِهِ؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> مَا يُعْجِبُنِي أَنَّهُ رجع فِي شَيْءٍ مِنْهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> وَلِمَ؟<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> عُمَرُ نَهَاهُ النَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ فِي الْفَرَسِ أَنْ يَرْجِعَ فِيهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ:</span> هُوَ بَيِّنٌ جَعَلَهُ لِلَّهِ يُكْرَهُ أَنْ يَرْجِعَ فِي شَيْءٍ مِنْهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَهَذَا هُوَ قَوْلٌ مِنْهُ وَلَيْسَ مِثْلَهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>⦗٩٤⦘<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ:</span> وَلَكِنَّ ابْنَ عُمَرَ <span class="c2">(.. ..)</span> اشْتَرَى صَدَقَتَهُ النَّهْيُ فِيهِ؟<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> نَعَمْ فَيُكْرَهُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> إِنِّي أُخْبِرُكَ مَا يُعْجِبُنِي أَنْ يَشْتَرِي مِنْهَا شَيْئًا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فَيَتَرَادَّانِ الْفَضْلَ؟<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ يَتَرَادَّانِ الْفَضْلَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فَإِذَا تَرَادَّا الْفَضْلَ لِمَ لَا يَشْتَرِي؟<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ لِي:</span> يَتَرَادَّانِ الْفَضْلَ لِشَيْءٍ <span class="c2">(.. ..)</span> فِي شَيْءٍ يُرَدُّ بِهِ وَيُأْخَذُ فَضْلُهُ وَهَذَا لَيْسَ مِنْ ذَاكَ يَشْتَرِيهَا.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> فِيهَا سُنَّةٌ؟<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ. حَدِيثُ حَمَّادِ بْنِ سَلَمَةَ وَهُوَ حَسَنٌ يَعْنِي حَدِيثَ ثُمَامَةَ فِي الصَّدَقَاتِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>